sequenceDiagram
    actor Applicant
    participant Frontend
    participant Gateway
    participant ApplicationService
    participant DocumentService

    Applicant->>Frontend: Fill loan application form
    Frontend->>Gateway: POST /gateway/applications
    Gateway->>ApplicationService: POST /api/applications
    ApplicationService-->>Gateway: 201 Created (draft app id)
    Gateway-->>Frontend: 201 Created
    Frontend-->>Applicant: Show saved draft / application id

    Applicant->>Frontend: Upload required documents
    Frontend->>Gateway: POST /gateway/documents/upload
    Gateway->>DocumentService: POST /api/document/upload
    DocumentService-->>Gateway: 200 OK
    Gateway-->>Frontend: 200 OK
    Frontend->>Gateway: GET /gateway/documents/{applicationId}/required
    Gateway->>DocumentService: GET /api/document/application/{applicationId}/required
    DocumentService-->>Gateway: 200 OK (checklist status)
    Gateway-->>Frontend: 200 OK

    Applicant->>Frontend: Click submit application
    Frontend->>Gateway: POST /gateway/applications/{id}/submit
    Gateway->>ApplicationService: POST /api/applications/{id}/submit
    ApplicationService-->>Gateway: 200 OK (submitted)
    Gateway-->>Frontend: 200 OK
    Frontend-->>Applicant: Show submission confirmation
